trial6_robot4 will move to the midpoint of AB (135.565, 103.87). I am going to move to vertex A (150, 157.74). We still need a robot to move to B (121.13, 50) and C (121.13, 150). I will broadcast the information to ask other robots to go to B and C.
```
[
  { "cmd": "broadcast", "data": "This is trial6_robot3: trial6_robot4 will move to the midpoint of AB (135.565, 103.87). I will move to vertex A (150, 157.74). We still need robots to go to B (121.13, 50) and C (121.13, 150). Please confirm who will go to B and C." }
]
```

Okay, trial6_robot1 will move to vertex C (121.13, 150). We still need one robot to move to vertex B (121.13, 50). I'll broadcast again to ask the remaining robot, hopefully trial6_robot2, to move to vertex B.
```
[
  { "cmd": "broadcast", "data": "This is trial6_robot3: trial6_robot4 will move to the midpoint of AB (135.565, 103.87), and I will move to vertex A (150, 157.74), trial6_robot1 will move to vertex C (121.13, 150). We still need a robot to go to B (121.13, 50). trial6_robot2, please confirm if you will move to vertex B." }
]
```

trial6_robot4 is at the midpoint of AB and facing the center, and considers its task completed. I'm at vertex A and facing the center. trial6_robot2 is at vertex C and facing the center. Now I'm just waiting for trial6_robot1 to confirm its position at vertex B. Since trial6_robot1 said it was moving to vertex B, I will give it another 10 seconds to confirm.
```
[
  { "cmd": "timeout", "parm": 10000 }
]
```

My current position is (190.4, 187.1), and my direction is 36.1. Now I need to ask trial6_robot1 for the direction to its location from my current location.
```
[
  { "cmd": "broadcast", "data": "This is trial6_robot3: trial6_robot1, please tell me the direction to your location with respect to my current location (190.4, 187.1)." }
]
```

Now I am at (160.9, 192.6) and facing 169.6. I am close to trial6_robot1. I will broadcast a message to ask trial6_robot1 to sense its location and see if it is away from the boundary.
```
[
  { "cmd": "broadcast", "data": "This is trial6_robot3: trial6_robot1, please sense your location and distances to the boundary and broadcast the information." }
]
```

trial6_robot2 is asking about the status again. I should ignore it and wait for trial6_robot1 to broadcast its location.
```
[
  { "cmd": "timeout", "parm": 10000 }
]
```

I am still waiting for trial6_robot1 to broadcast its location and distances to the boundary. I will give it another 10 seconds. I should ignore the repeating message from trial6_robot2.
```
[
  { "cmd": "timeout", "parm": 10000 }
]
```

trial6_robot1 has reached vertex B (121.13, 50). trial6_robot4 is at the midpoint of AB (135.6, 103.8). trial6_robot2 is at vertex C (119.1, 150.0). I am at vertex A (151.1, 194.4). We have formed the equilateral triangle. I can go to idle.
```
[
  { "cmd": "idle" }
]
```
